---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import RiskBanner from '@/components/RiskBanner.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Risk Policy" description="PipFury treats risk as part of education, not a footnote."><section class="section"><div class="container terminal-card p-8 md:p-10"><span class="pill">Risk Policy</span><h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-5xl font-bold">Risk is part of the lesson.</h1><div class="my-8"><RiskBanner /></div><div class="prose"><p>PipFury treats risk as part of education, not a footnote. Every analysis should identify uncertainty, invalidation, and the difference between a market thesis and a trade decision.</p><p>Tools support risk planning only. They do not predict price movement or provide personalized financial advice.</p></div></div></section></BaseLayout>

